<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>netstandard2.0</TargetFramework>
    <LangVersion>7.3</LangVersion>
    <RootNamespace>FunctionZero.MvvmZero</RootNamespace>
    <AssemblyName>FunctionZero.MvvmZero</AssemblyName>
    <Version>2.2.4-pre1</Version>
    <Copyright>FunctionZero Ltd. 2021</Copyright>
    <Description>An easy to use library for building cross-platform Xamarin Forms applications very quickly. Includes FunctionZero.zBind, allowing fully featured databinding to expressions.</Description>
    <PackageLicenseExpression></PackageLicenseExpression>
    <PackageLicenseFile>License.txt</PackageLicenseFile>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://github.com/Keflon/FunctionZero.MvvmZero</PackageProjectUrl>
    <PackageTags>Mvvm Xamarin Forms iOS UWP Android ICommand Command CommandZero CommandZeroAsync zbind expression parser databinding</PackageTags>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>Breaking change:
- Renamed OwnerPageAppearing to OnOwnerPageAppearing.
- Renamed OwnerPageDisappearing to OnOwnerPageDisappearing.

Bugfix:
PopToRootAsync now ensures the topmost Page calls OwnerPageDisappearing on its ViewModel if the Page's ViewModel supports IHasOwnerPage.
(Xamarin Forms does not inform the top page it is disappearing if Navigation.PopToRootAsync is called.)

New feature:
- Added AddPageTimer call to MvvmZeroBaseVm.
- - Adds a page timer that is only active whilst the page is presented. Experimental.
- IHasOwnerPage now supports INPC.</PackageReleaseNotes>
    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/Keflon/FunctionZero.MvvmZero</RepositoryUrl>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <PackageReference Include="FunctionZero.CommandZero" Version="1.1.0" />
    <PackageReference Include="FunctionZero.zBind" Version="1.2.1" />
    <PackageReference Include="Xamarin.Forms" Version="5.0.0.2012" />
  </ItemGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <None Include="License.txt">
      <Pack>True</Pack>
      <PackagePath></PackagePath>
    </None>
  </ItemGroup>

</Project>
